abstract: The president had joked about a conversation with Ms. Dingell after the death of her husband, former congressman John Dingell, at a rally in Michigan.
snippet: The president had joked about a conversation with Ms. Dingell after the death of her husband, former congressman John Dingell, at a rally in Michigan.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — One widow instantly knew how the other one felt.
